755
00:59:08,700 --> 00:59:14,880
Scallion kimchi, Godeulpaegi kimchi, fresh kimchi. Her orders never end!

756
00:59:16,600 --> 00:59:21,500
Sure! It's been a while, but I'll make it.

757
00:59:21,540 --> 00:59:24,630
Really? Gi Ja!

758
00:59:24,630 --> 00:59:29,310
I only have you, Gi Ja.

759
00:59:32,450 --> 00:59:34,310
Then peel some of these.

760
00:59:34,310 --> 00:59:38,060
The caller you are trying to reach is off...

761
00:59:38,060 --> 00:59:41,770
What's going on? Jenny's not even picking up her phone.

762
00:59:41,770 --> 00:59:44,770
Do I have to call Chief Jo?

763
00:59:46,660 --> 00:59:49,100
Ms. Park.

764
00:59:49,100 --> 00:59:51,990
Is something wrong?

765
00:59:51,990 --> 00:59:54,770
The thing is...

766
00:59:54,770 --> 01:00:00,490
Chairman, the truth is Jenny hasn't come home yet.

767
01:00:00,530 --> 01:00:03,660
What? What about the other children?

768
01:00:03,660 --> 01:00:07,630
Se Jong is sleeping, and Se Chan is washing up after finishing his homework.

769
01:00:07,630 --> 01:00:10,490
But Jenny isn't home and not picking her phone up.

770
01:00:10,490 --> 01:00:13,040
Is she not picking up her phone?

771
01:00:14,690 --> 01:00:18,080
Her last schedule is the English academy.

772
01:00:18,080 --> 01:00:20,830
I called the academy,

773
01:00:20,830 --> 01:00:24,870
and they said that it had been over two hours since the class ended.

774
01:00:24,890 --> 01:00:27,360
Over two hours?

775
01:00:27,360 --> 01:00:30,310
But why haven't you reported this to me until now?

776
01:00:30,310 --> 01:00:37,050
I thought she'd come home soon if I waited. But I must have thought wrong.

777
01:00:37,080 --> 01:00:40,900
Ms. Park, how can you do your job like this?

778
01:00:40,900 --> 01:00:45,610
I'll look for Jenny outside, so call me if she comes home in the meantime.

779
01:00:45,610 --> 01:00:48,280
Okay.

780
01:00:59,540 --> 01:01:02,850
Lee Jenny. Do you know what time it is?

781
01:01:02,850 --> 01:01:08,270
It's been over two hours since your academy was over. What have you been doing all this time?

782
01:01:08,270 --> 01:01:10,530
I'm tired.

783
01:01:10,530 --> 01:01:14,410
Tell me where you have been until now!

784
01:01:14,410 --> 01:01:16,190
I don't want to.

785
01:01:16,190 --> 01:01:21,270
What? What did you say?

786
01:01:21,330 --> 01:01:26,520
Why? You don't report to me who you're with nor where you're going.

787
01:01:26,520 --> 01:01:29,440
I'm your Dad!

788
01:01:29,440 --> 01:01:33,690
Why are you acting like this when you don't even care about me?

789
01:01:33,690 --> 01:01:40,230
Also, what if you're my Dad? I don't want to talk with you. I'm tired!

790
01:01:53,820 --> 01:01:58,000
Everyone, please rest now.

791
01:01:58,030 --> 01:02:02,950
I feel bad for our Chairman.

792
01:02:14,830 --> 01:02:16,600
What is it?

793
01:02:16,600 --> 01:02:19,590
Jenny. Do you have something going on?

794
01:02:19,590 --> 01:02:26,160
I saw dirt on your uniform earlier.

795
01:02:26,160 --> 01:02:27,840
Did you trip over?

796
01:02:27,840 --> 01:02:32,070
Can you close the door and leave? Stop bothering me.

797
01:02:35,820 --> 01:02:39,690
Okay, I will.

798
01:02:52,580 --> 01:02:55,240
What should I do?

799
01:02:55,240 --> 01:02:58,050
Will I get fired?

800
01:02:58,050 --> 01:03:01,720
I can't get fired.

801
01:03:01,720 --> 01:03:07,750
I promised Se Jong to be with him for a long time.

802
01:03:18,080 --> 01:03:20,460
Come on, Teacher!

803
01:03:20,460 --> 01:03:23,770
Alright, hold on a second!

804
01:03:23,770 --> 01:03:26,400
Let's go together!

805
01:03:29,050 --> 01:03:32,070
Come and find me!

806
01:03:36,400 --> 01:03:40,640
Do you think I can't find you?

807
01:03:40,640 --> 01:03:45,730
Where did Se Jong go?

808
01:03:45,730 --> 01:03:48,620
We're going to be late for kindergarten.

809
01:03:48,620 --> 01:03:51,630
The teacher said she'd be waiting for Se Jong.

810
01:03:51,630 --> 01:03:55,320
She said there would be delicious snacks today.

811
01:03:55,320 --> 01:04:00,190
Oh, what should I do if I can't find Se Jong? What a shame!

812
01:04:00,190 --> 01:04:03,090
Ta-da!

813
01:04:03,090 --> 01:04:06,010
Oh, my goodness! Where were you hiding?

814
01:04:06,010 --> 01:04:08,210
Let's go to kindergarten, hurry!

815
01:04:08,210 --> 01:04:10,840
Alright. Let's go.

816
01:04:10,840 --> 01:04:13,860
Oh, Se Jong, you should walk slowly! You'll trip!

817
01:04:13,860 --> 01:04:16,770
Walk slowly!

818
01:04:19,820 --> 01:04:25,300
What? Did I just dream about Dan Dan?

819
01:04:25,320 --> 01:04:29,310
I'm sure I heard Dan Dan just now.

820
01:04:29,310 --> 01:04:31,810
Honey! Dear.

821
01:04:31,810 --> 01:04:36,110
Didn't you hear Dan Dan's voice just now?

822
01:04:36,120 --> 01:04:37,760
What are you talking about?

823
01:04:37,760 --> 01:04:39,940
Why would you hear Dan Dan here?

824
01:04:39,940 --> 01:04:42,990
Oh, that's strange. I'm sure that was Dan Dan's voice.

825
01:04:42,990 --> 01:04:45,530
I fell asleep just now,

826
01:04:45,530 --> 01:04:50,100
but I heard Dan Dan saying, "let's go together," and her laughter.

827
01:04:50,100 --> 01:04:52,670
You must have dreamt it.

828
01:04:52,670 --> 01:04:58,850
Honey, I think I'm even dreaming about her since I'm very worried about Dan Dan.

829
01:04:58,850 --> 01:05:04,110
Honey, she's going to be okay, right?

830
01:05:04,110 --> 01:05:08,480
Dan Dan will do well anywhere. Don't worry.

831
01:05:16,100 --> 01:05:17,630
Who is it?

832
01:05:17,630 --> 01:05:21,630
Mr. Park! It's me, Mrs. Yeoju.

833
01:05:21,670 --> 01:05:25,380
Ah, yes! Hold on a moment, please.

834
01:05:25,410 --> 01:05:29,700
I made some short-rib stew this morning, and it turned out so well.

835
01:05:29,700 --> 01:05:33,040
So I wanted to share it with you, Mr. Park.

836
01:05:33,040 --> 01:05:35,550
Ah, yes. Thank you!

837
01:05:35,550 --> 01:05:37,260
If you need some more, please let me know.

838
01:05:37,260 --> 01:05:39,020
I'll bring you some more.

839
01:05:39,020 --> 01:05:42,940
Ah. No, no! This is more than enough!

840
01:05:45,860 --> 01:05:50,290
Can I have a cup of coffee here?

841
01:05:50,290 --> 01:05:54,730
What are those two doing?

842
01:05:54,760 --> 01:06:01,370
I have a bit of time right now.

843
01:06:01,370 --> 01:06:04,980
Right now, I have something urgent to check at the bank.

844
01:06:04,980 --> 01:06:07,790
I was going to hurry there and come back before the Madam called for me.

845
01:06:07,790 --> 01:06:12,420
Can we have coffee next time?

846
01:06:12,420 --> 01:06:15,040
Is that so?

847
01:06:15,040 --> 01:06:17,470
Well, that's a shame.

848
01:06:17,470 --> 01:06:20,920
- Let's have coffee together next time.
- Sure.

849
01:06:20,920 --> 01:06:24,290
Thank you for the food.

850
01:06:30,510 --> 01:06:32,670
Honey.

851
01:06:32,670 --> 01:06:36,620
Did that woman just flirt with you?

852
01:06:36,620 --> 01:06:38,350
Lower your voice!

853
01:06:38,350 --> 01:06:41,770
What kind of crazy foxy woman is she?

854
01:06:41,770 --> 01:06:45,930
What? "Can I have a cup of coffee here?" Is she crazy?

855
01:06:45,930 --> 01:06:48,040
I said you should lower your voice!

856
01:06:48,040 --> 01:06:49,840
Wait.

857
01:06:49,840 --> 01:06:54,370
Have you been telling me to leave because of that woman?

858
01:06:54,370 --> 01:06:59,260
You were planning to drink coffee with that woman, so you wanted me out?

859
01:06:59,260 --> 01:07:00,570
You--!

860
01:07:00,570 --> 01:07:02,760
I'm telling you this for sure,

861
01:07:02,760 --> 01:07:08,770
but I'm never going to leave this place on my own! Did you understand me?

862
01:07:14,890 --> 01:07:18,620
Why don't you open the short-rib stew pot?

863
01:07:18,620 --> 01:07:21,030
Here. Here.

864
01:07:28,910 --> 01:07:30,740
Why aren't you going in?

865
01:07:30,750 --> 01:07:35,090
Teacher. You're going to pick me up later, right?

866
01:07:35,090 --> 01:07:37,280
You're not going somewhere far, are you?

867
01:07:37,280 --> 01:07:40,710
Of course! I'll pick you up later, Se Jong.

868
01:07:40,710 --> 01:07:43,650
So don't worry.

869
01:07:43,650 --> 01:07:52,220
Teacher. Are you going to keep the promise that you're going to stay with me for a long time?

870
01:07:52,220 --> 01:07:56,740
Of course. We made a pinky promise.

871
01:07:56,740 --> 01:08:03,730
I'll stay next to Se Jong for a very, very long time!

872
01:08:15,980 --> 01:08:22,410
Right. I need to work harder for Se Jong, who believes in me.

873
01:08:22,430 --> 01:08:26,540
Let's try harder, Park Dan Dan!

874
01:08:26,540 --> 01:08:31,030
Oh, Ms. Park! Can you bring this fresh kimchi to Mr. Park?

875
01:08:31,030 --> 01:08:34,390
Say hi to him while you're there. You haven't seen him yet, have you?

876
01:08:34,390 --> 01:08:36,970
Yes. I will.

877
01:08:46,540 --> 01:08:49,660
That crazy fox must have come back.

878
01:08:49,660 --> 01:08:52,130
- Go!
- Okay.

879
01:08:54,390 --> 01:08:58,770
You better reject her. Tell her you can't drink coffee together because you have a wife.

880
01:08:58,770 --> 01:09:00,760
I said, get inside!

881
01:09:00,760 --> 01:09:03,710
- Alright!
- Get inside!

882
01:09:07,180 --> 01:09:08,970
Who is it?

883
01:09:08,970 --> 01:09:12,380
I'm here to deliver something from Mrs. Yeoju.

884
01:09:14,630 --> 01:09:18,700
Isn't that Dan Dan's voice?

885
01:09:18,700 --> 01:09:21,660
I said, go inside!

886
01:09:25,220 --> 01:09:29,050
Alright. Just a moment!

887
01:09:32,630 --> 01:09:36,350
Hello, I'm Park Dan Dan--

888
01:09:38,220 --> 01:09:42,710
D-Dan Dan?

889
01:09:42,710 --> 01:09:44,580
Dad?

890
01:09:44,580 --> 01:09:49,500
Oh! Oh my, look who's here!

891
01:09:49,500 --> 01:09:52,200
It's really Dan Dan!

892
01:09:52,200 --> 01:09:54,500
Mom?

893
01:10:04,810 --> 01:10:11,640
♫ A smile runs to me in every step ♫

894
01:10:11,680 --> 01:10:18,220
♫ It's a shiny day because of you ♫

895
01:10:18,220 --> 01:10:25,450
♫ Strangely, I'm drawn to you ♫

896
01:10:25,450 --> 01:10:28,290
♫ Nobody will understand me ♫

897
01:10:28,290 --> 01:10:34,230
♫ You're the one that I was looking for ♫

898
01:10:34,230 --> 01:10:37,400
[Young Lady and Gentleman]

899
01:10:37,400 --> 01:10:39,610
What are you doing, hiding in someone else's house?

900
01:10:39,610 --> 01:10:41,550
Mom, do you ever think before doing something?

901
01:10:41,550 --> 01:10:44,670
It's better for one person to survive rather than both getting fired.

902
01:10:44,670 --> 01:10:47,970
I can't leave. So you leave, Dad.

903
01:10:47,970 --> 01:10:50,600
I can't live off of you forever. I'm Park Dae Beom.

904
01:10:50,600 --> 01:10:52,310
Baby, are you doing this because you can't trust me?

905
01:10:52,310 --> 01:10:54,440
Is he the Mi So Steel company's son? Really?

906
01:10:54,440 --> 01:10:57,320
I think I'll have to step in for our Gook Hee and Young Gook.

907
01:10:57,320 --> 01:11:00,550
So why did you give them the kimchi I made? Why!

908
01:11:00,550 --> 01:11:05,140
Unni, stop lingering around the Chairman with the excuse of being his friend!

909
01:11:05,140 --> 01:11:07,750
Who do you think you are to get rid of my Mom's stuff, Dad!

910
01:11:07,750 --> 01:11:09,460
Do you have a new woman? Is that why?

911
01:11:09,460 --> 01:11:12,490
Chairman! Children have their pains and their own emotions!

912
01:11:12,490 --> 01:11:15,210
- Lee Jenny. Tell me the truth.
- Don't tell my dad!

913
01:11:15,210 --> 01:11:18,260
Ms. Park! I said, you should tell me!
